

1.  go to the portal.azure.com
2.  then click create resources
3.  search for Web App
4.  select resource group / java 11 / SE and all / service plan as West Europe

5.  then after that you can go to the resource group and check it out your Web App 
    there in web app there were lot of option like : brouse / logs you can check 
    / configuration / start and stop web app

6.  in deployment center you can check how you want to deploy your code 
    like from GitHub, Azure Repos, CI/CD pipeline

